The aim of the project is to create an UI for gathering data which will stored and rendered into diffrient layout templates.
Project consist of 3 parts:
1) Create an interface and MVC architecture to gather and store data, in a form that will be accessible for templates controllers.
2) Create an interface for saving the data localy
3) Create templates that will work with the data

Done:
  (1) Interface for creating JSON which stores data for template.
  (2) Saving using local store HTML5 API.

Current state (2):
  Creating unit tests with Karma.
  Adding functionality of loading from a local drive.
  
Next step to do:
  Choose better colors
  
Working demo:
  http://www.pureepic.eu/angular/creator
  
